{"tid":160020,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"靚叉燒","createTime":"2017-03-17T11:45:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-23T03:58:47.000Z","uid":62277,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b46948c558756714b5480424350eb8eecbbc88b8","tid":160020,"uid":62277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T11:45:41.000Z","msg":"之前都係食開25蚊叉飯<br />\n今次試下就咁買30蚊叉<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/17/194258_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F17%2F194258_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=9e11e63d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n水準都算係咁<br />\n有肥有燶,燒得香<br />\n腍度、蜜味都適中<br />\n肉既腌味偏重少少<br />\n如果有返d鮮味就更加好<br />\n下次都係就咁叫叉飯,<br />\n唔洗浸汁咁耐,無咁濃味<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/17/194343_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F17%2F194343_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=b60abf86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nbtw,食過最正嘅叉燒都係上環龍邦<br />\n可惜嗰度水準不穩,要撞彩"},{"pid":"5019cd3d44bc91d94266dfc10c7a2c2d5365e657","tid":160020,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T11:50:03.000Z","msg":"好正呀，見到好肚餓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"350048309c6ba3848ac8035b52e9cd650abf46f0","tid":160020,"uid":50323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T11:52:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"711d3d85c8d5c3e9c3580975f32c228921d2cca6","tid":160020,"uid":34489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-17T12:20:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"464ef6